author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Insperity Q4 Earnings Per Share $0.36
text:
Feb 12 (Reuters) - Insperity Inc:
* INSPERITY ANNOUNCES RECORD FOURTH QUARTER AND FULL YEAR 2017 RESULTS
* Q4 ADJUSTED EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.55 * Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.36 * Q4 REVENUE ROSE 13 PERCENT TO $826.5 MILLION * SEES Q1 2018 ADJUSTED EPS $1.12 - $1.16
* SEES FY 2018 ADJUSTED EPS $2.96 - $3.08
* Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.46, REVENUE VIEW $813.2 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $1.09 -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
